name: Space Ops (YaBoyLED)
description:
A ship has crashed on the planet of Zebulun, and you are the last remaining survivor on the ship. Nanobots create an infusion, cause you to join together with the remains of the creatures that are infiltrating the spaceship. The goal: to survive.

Controls: WASD, Fuse with body parts: F, Shoot/Aim: Mouse and Click

Please follow these amazing, talented people on their journey to greatness.
